SUB_W09_EVAR_SIUG_OPENING_120_CUT_000_05.text:
Oh, I'm nothing so special;
merely a prisoner of the royals
and nothing more.

SUB_W09_EVAR_SIUG_OPENING_130_CUT_020_04.text:
True darkness is not born of ignorance;
I suspect Her Majesty understands all
and is simply playing a part.

SUB_W09_EVAR_SIUG_LAST_200_CUT_000_010.text:
Spare me your counsel and step aside;
I've brought a cracking offering that
is certain to please His Majesty.
